title: PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs
text: > Top News PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs FILE - At left, in an Oct. 20, 2015, file photo, New York Mets' Daniel Murphy celebrates after hitting his sixth 2015 postseason home run, during the third inning of Game 3 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs in Chicago. At right, Mets' Daniel Murphy hits the home run during the third inning of Game 3 of the National League baseball championship series against the Cubs in Chicago. Murphy won NL Championship Series MVP on Wednesday night, Oct. 21, 2015, after homering for a postseason-record sixth straight game, leading the Mets over the Chicago Cubs 8-3 to complete a four-game sweep. (AP Photo/File)
